" fill in empty markdown links with duck.com search
" [some thing]() -> [some thing](https://duck.com/lite?kae=t&q=some thing)
autocmd vimleavepre *.md !perl -p -i -e 's,\[([^\]]+?)\]\(\),[\1](https://duck.com/lite?q=\1),g' %

